Package nl.b3p.brmo.util

Class CountingSeekableByteChannel

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.b3p.brmo.util.CountingSeekableByteChannel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, ByteChannel, Channel, ReadableByteChannel, SeekableByteChannel, WritableByteChannel
    public class CountingSeekableByteChannel
extends Object
implements SeekableByteChannel
    Analogous to a CountingInputStream, this wraps a channel and records the number of bytes read and written in addition to the number of non-consecutive reads or writes.

    Optionally the bytes read can be printed to System.out (requires commons-codec).

    Author:
    Matthijs Laan
